# Base URL the SPA calls for the Laravel API. In local dev, the Vite dev
# server proxies /api to VITE_API_PROXY_TARGET (see vite.config.ts) so this
# can stay unset. In production, point it at wherever hostinger-app is
# deployed, e.g. https://api.jubileewater.example/api or /api if the SPA and
# API share the same domain behind a reverse proxy.
VITE_API_URL=/api
